<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩٢٧ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا مُسَدَّدٌ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى بْنُ سَعِيدٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ:</span> أَخْبَرَنِي نَافِعٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">أَنَّ عُمَرَ سَأَلَ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> كُنْتُ نَذَرْتُ فِي الْجَاهِلِيَّةِ أَنْ أَعْتَكِفَ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗٧١٥⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَيْلَةً فِي الْمَسْجِدِ الْحَرَامِ؟.<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(فَأَوْفِ بِنَذْرِكَ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
